            "\u201cAt that time I commanded you all the things that you were to do.",
            "\u201cThen we set out from Horeb, and went through all that great and terrible wilderness that you saw on the way to the hill country of the Amorites, just as the LORD our God had commanded us; and we came to Kadesh-barnea.",
